fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.inout.importer

Class DIPToArchiveDeliveryRequestReplyImporter

  • Object
    • DIPToArchiveDeliveryRequestReplyImporter

  • public class DIPToArchiveDeliveryRequestReplyImporter
extends Object
    The Class DIPToArchiveDeliveryRequestReplyImporter.

    Class for SEDA Dissemination Information Packet (DIP) import in ArchiveDeliveryRequestReply object. Elements not used in Vitam DIPs, for the moment, are not supported in this import.
